quran[33]{c,v,t}:
  55,46,And for him who feared to stand before his Fosterer are two gardens
  55,47,So which of the bounties of your Fosterer will you both deny
  55,48,Having in them various kinds
  55,49,So which of the bounties of your Fosterer will you both deny
  55,50,In both of them are flowing springs
  55,51,So which of the bounties of your Fosterer will you both deny
  55,52,In both of them every (kind) of fruit will be in two pairs
  55,53,So which of the bounties of your Fosterer will you both deny
  55,54,"Reclining on spreadings (like bed sheets, carpets etc.) the inner linings of which will be of silk brocade, and the fruits of the two gardens will be near"
  55,55,So which of the bounties of your Fosterer will you both deny
  55,56,"In both of them will be females who restrain their gaze, whom neither man nor jinn touched before them"
  55,57,So which of the bounties of your Fosterer will you both deny
  55,58,As if they were rubies and corals
  55,59,So which of the bounties of your Fosterer will you both deny
  55,60,Is the reward of good (something) other than good
  55,61,So which of the bounties of your Fosterer will you both deny
  55,62,"And besides these two, are two more gardens"
  55,63,So which of the bounties of your Fosterer will you both deny
  55,64,"Both, dark green in colour"
  55,65,So which of the bounties of your Fosterer will you both deny
  55,66,In both of them are two springs gushing forth
  55,67,So which of the bounties of your Fosterer will you both deny
  55,68,In both of them are fruits and date palms and pomegranates
  55,69,So which of the bounties of your Fosterer will you both deny
  55,70,In both of them are good and beautiful ones
  55,71,So which of the bounties of your Fosterer will you both deny
  55,72,"Fair ones, confined in pavilions"
  55,73,So which of the bounties of your Fosterer will you both deny
  55,74,Whom neither man nor jinn touched before them
  55,75,So which of the bounties of your Fosterer will you both deny
  55,76,Reclining on green cushions and beautiful carpets
  55,77,So which of the bounties of your Fosterer will you both deny
  55,78,"Blessed is the name of your Fosterer, Possessor of glory and honour"